ENTER ROUTE CODE!                                                      03
DOCK CODE IS BLANK. IF IT'S OK, PRESS ENTER KEY AGAIN.                 04
ENTER DELLIVERY CODE!                                                  05
ENTER EFFECTIVE DATE!                                                  06
DELIVERY CODE DOES NOT EXIST IN FORD ROUTES MASTER(ABFDP01)!           07
ENTER VALID FROM DATE!                                                 08
PRESS F5 TO UPDATE...                                                  09
ENTER PLANT CODE!                                                      10
DUPLICATE KEYS FOUND! CHECK <DELIBERY# + DOCK + IC CODE>.              11
                                                                       12
